Get the coordinates.

389
00:47:02,560 --> 00:47:07,190
- They're splitting up.
- 64.5, 32.0.

390
00:47:07,360 --> 00:47:11,273
Aim at the place
that's been used as a firing point.

391
00:47:18,880 --> 00:47:22,316
Do they have to assemble
the gun first or what?

392
00:47:22,480 --> 00:47:24,869
9-0. Pancake.

393
00:47:27,680 --> 00:47:30,831
- Alright!
- About bloody time.

394
00:49:06,800 --> 00:49:11,237
- Do you want everyone to meet up?
- Yes ...

395
00:49:11,400 --> 00:49:14,597
2nd platoon, at the vehicles.

396
00:49:14,760 --> 00:49:18,196
There he is! Our man.

397
00:49:18,360 --> 00:49:21,955
- Alright?
- You bet. I'm in great shape.

398
00:49:22,120 --> 00:49:25,749
- Hi, guys.
- You smell good, too.

399
00:49:25,920 --> 00:49:30,118
- But you don't.
- Hello!

400
00:49:31,160 --> 00:49:34,118
- Nice to see you.
- Hey, man.

401
00:49:34,280 --> 00:49:39,877
I'm sick of hugging sweaty guys by
now. Who else? Jesus Christ.

402
00:49:40,040 --> 00:49:42,554
Hey, guys.
Are we all here?

403
00:49:44,680 --> 00:49:46,671
Hey, man.

404
00:49:46,840 --> 00:49:51,550
- I'm glad you grew that beard again.
- I thought you might feel that way.

405
00:49:53,080 --> 00:49:56,117
- Here's group leader 1.
- Well, for the time being.

406
00:49:56,280 --> 00:50:00,637
It's fucking great to see you guys.
Any questions?

407
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:03,519
Great. Let's go.

408
00:50:10,960 --> 00:50:14,635
Signaler, the locals say the Taliban
bugged out north and south -

409
00:50:14,800 --> 00:50:17,155
- when they saw us arrive.

410
00:50:22,120 --> 00:50:25,829
Signaler, will you cover me
if I run out in the field?

411
00:50:26,000 --> 00:50:29,356
- Probably not.
- This is damn depressing.

412
00:50:29,520 --> 00:50:34,878
All dressed up
and no one to blow. This won't do.

413
00:50:35,040 --> 00:50:39,477
- Wanna bet?
- Nothing will happen.

414
00:50:39,640 --> 00:50:43,997
Nothing will happen?
It's no fun betting when we agree.

415
00:50:47,280 --> 00:50:52,479
Daniel, how about stripping
and running naked across the field?

416
00:50:52,640 --> 00:50:58,158
- That might kick things up a notch.
- His pink body will scare them off.

417
00:50:59,320 --> 00:51:02,153
Shut the fuck up.

418
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:07,276
The other day ...
My house was bombed.

419
00:51:07,440 --> 00:51:12,434
My cow was killed,
and two calves.

420
00:51:12,600 --> 00:51:15,558
They didn't die,
they were wounded.

421
00:51:15,720 --> 00:51:18,553
A cow was killed.
