429
00:51:56,320 --> 00:52:00,836
But it's important
that we collaborate.

430
00:52:01,000 --> 00:52:04,037
So we can make peace here.

431
00:52:04,200 --> 00:52:09,513
God willing, we can bring peace
to this place. Rebuild the country ...

432
00:52:09,680 --> 00:52:14,674
Exactly, but we'll see.
God will provide.

433
00:52:14,840 --> 00:52:18,958
We ... the country is exhausted.

434
00:52:23,200 --> 00:52:28,115
2-1, can we move forward,
or do we wait?

435
00:52:28,280 --> 00:52:33,673
- Having a nice time?
- We don't have to cuddle up.

436
00:52:33,840 --> 00:52:38,755
Unless you want to.
I have a hole in my pants.

437
00:52:40,760 --> 00:52:44,196
I can use my finger if you like?

438
00:52:46,000 --> 00:52:50,710
- You missed. A bit further up.
