448
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:52,798
- Should we take it and crush them?
- Daniel? New plan.

449
00:53:52,960 --> 00:53:57,556
Two guys in Sierra 5.
Right there!

450
00:53:57,720 --> 00:54:01,156
- Do you want explosives?
