451
00:54:01,320 --> 00:54:06,075
There's still that hole in the wall.
The hole straight ahead.

452
00:54:22,680 --> 00:54:27,515
Proceed. I got it here.
Get in front.

453
00:54:28,920 --> 00:54:31,275
There's something here.

454
00:54:35,680 --> 00:54:38,148
There's a civilian.

455
00:54:53,920 --> 00:54:57,196
Forward.

456
00:54:58,920 --> 00:55:01,115
There's no one here.

457
00:55:01,280 --> 00:55:05,478
Civilians in the compound.
We will continue searching.

458
00:55:05,640 --> 00:55:08,677
There's no one here.

459
00:55:08,840 --> 00:55:11,513
Salaam aleikum.

460
00:55:11,680 --> 00:55:14,911
901, 5 is searched. Out.

461
00:55:15,080 --> 00:55:19,039
Fuck, I'm tired of this shit.

462
00:55:20,760 --> 00:55:25,709
They're laughing at us, and we waste
time blasting into these compounds.

463
00:55:25,880 --> 00:55:29,270
And they're already gone.
A waste of time.

464
00:55:30,840 --> 00:55:35,834
- Mortar, another 15 ts.
- Ready ...!

465
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:38,639
Everybody ready ... shoot!

